Kiwi Kittens are a tiny minion that was used by [[Kiw]] himself. Kiwi kittens are ruthless and will devour anything that gets in the way of their path. Kiwi Kittens also have the ability to blend in with many different objects though mainly fruit and other vegetation. They mainly hide in farms and grocery stores. 

The estimate of kills every Kiwi Kitten has combined together is higher than Kiw's count himself. They are ruthless but they aren't monsters, they are known to befriend and help any other kittens enemy or not. They are nearly extinct with only about 150 left though its rapidly decreasing because of them being ruthlessly hunted  for being Kiws past followers, but they are also repopulating very quickly, due to their ability to lay camouflaged eggs. They soon manage to repopulate by 500, using photosynthesis. They slept next to kiwis (plant kiwis) and those Kiwis turned into Kiwi Kittens. It also worked on kiwi birds.

In the silly cats games they are enemies that appear in the forest. Some NPCs give you high reward quests if you manage steal their eggs but these quests are incredibly difficult with how dangerous the kiwi kittens are when their eggs are threatened by anybody. 

Later on in the series they fight in "War Of The Silly of Silly and Unsilly" since by then there are about 650 left, but only 50 were the originals.

They are villains, but they aren't monsters, and only hurt you if you try eat them, their young or their eggs.

After the war of silly and unsilly the remaining kiwi kittens went into hiding and tried to repopulate bringing their numbers back up to about 2000. due to their master Kiw being killed in the war they mostly took up simple lives creating a small village called [[Kiwiville]] near the cave system they hid in while repopulating. Though some left and took up lives of evil once more working for remaining [[B.A.D]] cells and other new evil organisations particularly [[George]]'s cohort{{Top|Canon}}

