On April 12, 2013, Dr. Pebba walked into a 7-Eleven in Miami, Florida demanding money whilst pointing a S&W Model 63 at the cashier, [[Harold]]. After Harold agreed to give Dr. Pebba the money, he immediately called the police, who apprehended Dr. Pebba while he was fleeing the scene in a 2009 Honda Civic. Dr. Pebba was sentenced to a year in prison. He was released on May 2, 2014. After and before this, he was kicked from F.A.C.T


==Silly Cats Online Quests==
In [[Silly Cats: Online|Silly Cats: Online]], Dr. Pebba will offer you to help him break into and explode a convenience store for refusing to promote the Dr. Pepper brand. Do this, and he will then give you a quest to destroy the Coca-Cola factory, Complete this task, and he rewards you with 2500 Silly Bucks.

