== Description ==
{{Character|image=PankoStare.png|name=Panko|imagecaption=Panko, with her well-known cross-eyed glare.|status={{Alive}}|nationality={{American}}|aliases=fatfatpankocat|relatives=Milly|affiliation=The Forsaken Territories|occupation=Governing all silliness within this known universe|gender=Female|breed=Forsaken|fur=Calico}}
Panko, best described, is not quite a material nor energetic being. Panko is a constant consciousness, always seeing, observing, and watching. Never directly revealing her form, yet always present. She is a member of the Forsaken Territories - a "council" of sorts that governs and oversees all activity of the cats; silly, bad, or otherwise skrunkly all take part in this. Panko's role of the Forsaken Territories is to oversee the "Silly" sector. In fact, Panko's own immortal paws formed the concept of silliness itself. Upon the birth of time as we know it, Panko formed Milly to be a greater, more conceptualizable figure to be known by the cats, as a demigod is to a god. Milly was formed using 4 essential ingredients, that being uranium, magic 8-ball fluid, opium, and chocolate. Milly was then sent into the universe in the birthplace known as the Ping Pong Table. Milly's sole job was to direct the silly cats out of bad's grasp, allowing them to grow to the most silly they could be. This revolutionized the concept of silliness as it is known today.

